title: Dead Celebrity Status Discography
description:
Dead Celebrity Status is a Punk/Rap group from Ontario, Canada. Both rappers are former members of Project Wyze. Blood music is a re-upload of Bonescraper's work (with slightly modified/upgraded tags and file names), and The Throwaway Kids (minus the youtube extended version) came from kingdomleaks. All of these files have accurate (and matching) id3 tags, written by me.
